name: Kyeltziv Technocracy Naval Assets Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the common ship hulls used by the Kyeltziv Technocracy.

name: Kyeltziv Technocracy Strikecraft Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the common strikecraft LPCs used by the Kyeltziv Technocracy.

name: Kyeltziv Technocracy Weapon Systems Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the common weapons used by the Kyeltziv Technocracy.

name: Kyeltziv Technocracy Export Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct export models of certain Kyeltziv Technocracy vessels.
